                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17640607-10-victim113 t17640607-10-viclabel65"></join>, and live in Spittal Fields. On the 11th of February, I delivered<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176406070007"></xptr> eleven pounds four ounces and a half of silk, to 
               <persName id="t17640607-10-person117">
                  John 
                  Cosins 
               <interp inst="t17640607-10-person117" type="surname" value="Cosins"></interp>
