                  </persName>
            . She owned to taking seven ounces: she said she sold some to a man that she did not know. Then we went to Hick's-hall, and got a warrant against 
               <persName id="t17640607-10-person121">
                  Anne 
                  Levins 
               <interp inst="t17640607-10-person121" type="surname" value="Levins"></interp>
